  * Dashboard: fix a web UI hang where the product info feed widget could
    stall the whole interface. The feed was fetched with no curl timeout, so
    a slow or unreachable host (e.g. an IPv6 address with no route) blocked
    the request up to the php-fpm terminate timeout (~125s) while holding the
    PHP session lock, serializing every other GUI request. Bounded the fetch
    with a 3s connect / 6s total timeout and pointed it at the MurOS feed.

